content.text: What do you do to relax?
I like to hike with my horses and eat ginger snaps along the way. It's so relaxing just being out in nature and spending time with my animals.
That sounds really nice, I don't have any horses so I've never been hiking with them. I love the outdoors though.
What kind of stuff do you do outdoors?
I like to go fishing and camping. I also like to build model airplanes and fly them.
That's cool, I've never been fishing but I've always wanted to try. I like camping too.
Fishing is really fun, you should definitely try it sometime. And yeah, camping is great. It's so peaceful being out in the wilderness.
I will have to try it sometime. And yeah, camping is really peaceful. I love just sitting around the campfire and listening to the sounds of the night.
That's what's great about camping, you can just relax and enjoy nature.
Yeah, it's the perfect way to get away from everything.
I agree. So, do you have any hobbies besides writing?
I like to listen to rap music. I'm also a big fan of YouTube.
That's cool, I like listening to rap music too. What are some of your favorite artists?
I like Kendrick Lamar, J. Cole, and Drake.
Those are all great artists, I like them too.
Yeah, they're all really talented.
So, what do you like to do on YouTube?
I like to watch music videos, funny videos, and vlogs.
That's cool, I like watching YouTube too. It's a great way to relax and be entertained.
Yeah, it is. I can watch YouTube for hours on end.
Me too. I've lost track of time a few times watching YouTube.
Yeah, it can be really addictive.
Definitely. So, what's your favorite thing to do on YouTube?
I like watching music videos. I love watching the artists perform their songs and seeing the behind-the-scenes footage.
That's cool, I like watching music videos too. It's a great way to see the artists' creative process.
Yeah, it is. I can watch music videos for hours on end.
Me too. I've lost track of time a few times watching YouTube.
Yeah, it can be really addictive.
